description: Available at https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Geoffrey credits the legendary pianist Hank Jones as a major influence on his style. This lesson examines Hank's intriguing reharmonization of the Duke Ellington classic "Satin Doll", and shows you how to apply similar harmonic concepts to standards like "Corcovado" and "Body and Soul". PDF included. (Level: Advanced)
title: Geoffrey Keezer - Hank Jones' "Satin Doll" (Preview)
